    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 26. Fedrizzia abradoalves sp. nov. 22, chelicera; 23, gnathosoma of female; 24, gnathosoma of male; 25, venter of female; 26, venter of male. Scale bar = 50 for 22 – 24; 100 for 25, 26." ;
