<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176848>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Gnathosomal region of male (A) Fedrizzia abradoalves sp. nov. and (B) Neofedrizzia vidua. Abbreviations: h 1 – 3 = hypostomal setae 1 – 3; av 1 = first anteroventral seta of palp trochanter. Arrow points to hypostomal tubercle. Scale bar = 10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176848/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

